text: The material relating to Technical Assistance and Technical Advice Requests previously contained in IRM 4.81.9, Tax Exempt Bonds, Examination Program and Procedures, Technical Assistance and Technical Advice Requests, is incorporated into new IRM 4.80.1, Indian Tribal Governments and Tax Exempt Bonds, Examination Program and Procedures, Technical Assistance and Technical Advice Requests. The new IRM provides procedures for employees working cases pertaining to Indian Tribal Governments and Tax Exempt Bonds.
